WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:01.051
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.051 --> 00:00:02.399
How y'all been doing?

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:03.164
I'm doing good.

00:00:03.164 --> 00:00:08.960
I just wanted to come on and tell you all some things that the Lord has been having me pray over.

00:00:09.226 --> 00:00:13.586
When I got in prayer, this is one of the things that he told me.

00:00:13.586 --> 00:00:23.360
He said, "I want you to watch Passover, for Passover will become a time of even more acceleration.

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:34.062
" There will be an even greater acceleration at the time of Passover.

00:00:38.430 --> 00:00:40.520
And then I said, "Acceleration of what?

00:00:43.075 --> 00:00:48.480
" He said, "My son's return for the bride is imminent.

00:00:52.284 --> 00:00:58.848
" I got so excited because the power of God hit me so strong when he said this.

00:00:59.124 --> 00:01:08.400
He said, "My son's return for the bride is imminent.

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.360
It's right there, son.

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:16.585
It's about to happen.

00:01:26.479 --> 00:01:27.631
" I felt such an urgency and an anticipation for what God was telling me.

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:33.257
He said, "There's an acceleration.

00:01:33.257 --> 00:01:45.480
You're going to see acceleration again from Passover going into the rest of the year.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:52.700
" This will be a time of great acceleration.

00:01:52.700 --> 00:02:04.595
So even from Rosh Hashanah, he said this would be a time of acceleration.

00:02:04.595 --> 00:02:48.000
But now he spoke to me and said from Passover to whenever—I don't know, he didn't give me a time frame—he just said this would be a time of even greater acceleration in the spirit realm, with the economy, signs, politics, all of it with Israel.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:58.256
Then he said this to me: "I want you to pay attention to the East.

00:02:58.256 --> 00:03:18.146
" I saw Chicago and Philadelphia, and through the summer, I saw headlines in the news and great heatwaves in the Northeast—record temperatures never seen before in that area.

00:03:21.390 --> 00:03:36.706
He said there will be record temperatures in Chicago and record temperatures in Philadelphia, and this would be a sign of the weather acceleration, the birthing pains of the earth, things like that.

00:03:36.706 --> 00:03:56.129
I saw heat like I hate because hot summers are terrible, but I saw a record-breaking summer up in Chicago.

00:04:04.199 --> 00:04:07.300
I don't know if it's a day of heat or if it's a long stretch.

00:04:14.955 --> 00:04:24.729
I just saw that it would be record-breaking temperatures for the summer in that area—maybe it lasts a week, maybe it lasts a month.

00:04:24.729 --> 00:04:34.571
I just saw record-breaking temperatures over Philadelphia, New York, and all up in the Northeast.

00:04:40.230 --> 00:04:49.340
Then he spoke to me about the thunderstorms again and told me there would be record-breaking wind gusts.

00:04:53.880 --> 00:05:00.260
I saw downbursts coming out of the storms—updrafts and the wind coming down.

00:05:00.260 --> 00:05:04.000
Straight-line winds over 150 mph.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:12.626
Not tornadic, but like when a thunderstorm collapses and has a burst of air.

00:05:13.332 --> 00:05:17.447
I saw 150 mph windbursts coming out like straight-line winds.

00:05:18.191 --> 00:05:29.045
The Lord was talking to me about storms coming in the spring, and like I told you, long-track tornadoes.

00:05:29.045 --> 00:05:34.111
Pray—we have authority over this now.

00:05:34.111 --> 00:05:39.090
I'm not telling you all this to freak you out.

00:05:39.090 --> 00:05:57.177
There are storms we can pray against and pray a hedge of protection around your area, your neighborhood, and over your home.

00:05:57.177 --> 00:06:01.320
No weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:16.280
Psalms 91 and Psalms 23—quoting those and getting ready because we're in an active time on this earth.

00:06:16.280 --> 00:06:39.240
He started talking to me about long-track supercells, superstorms that were going to try to happen in the spring through April, May, and June.

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.884
We're almost there.

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:00.000
I just thought it was interesting when he was talking to me about an acceleration at Passover because I was trying to figure out when Passover was.

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:03.800
It's at the end of April.

00:07:11.456 --> 00:07:11.879
That was just one night of prayer.

00:07:11.879 --> 00:07:31.600
He started showing me glimpses of headlines: glimpses of droughts in certain areas with no rain, and then for some areas, there was going to be a lot of rain in the spring.

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:41.280
I saw great downpours, the lakes and ponds filling up as a sign of mercy.

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:46.900
He started talking to me a lot about grace.

00:07:46.900 --> 00:07:56.329
It's something you don't earn; it's something you don't deserve, but it's just by his love.

00:07:56.329 --> 00:08:03.746
He was really working on my heart about not being so rigid.

00:08:03.746 --> 00:08:28.970
He was saying, "Brandon, there is a balance where you are not living in sin, but you need to understand, son, that it's not about your works and never will be.

00:08:28.970 --> 00:08:34.080
" Self-righteousness to him is a total stench.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:49.808
The Lord was correcting me because I'm not to be so focused on the law.

00:08:49.808 --> 00:08:59.709
There's a balance where people can walk out grace.

00:08:59.709 --> 00:09:15.120
He washed all our sins away, past, present, and future, but it's not practicing a lifestyle of sin.

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:25.119
I always want to come across in these videos as a grace man too.

00:09:25.119 --> 00:09:45.040
I love the Lord with all my heart, and I want to make sure people understand that I don't want them to go to hell.

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:58.068
I don't want them to think that they can live a life of sin and still make the Rapture.

00:09:58.068 --> 00:10:00.090
It's about relationship.

00:10:02.540 --> 00:10:12.445
I don't have all my stuff together, but where sin abounds, grace does much more abound.

00:10:12.445 --> 00:10:19.515
I've been still praying for the hostages' release.

00:10:24.635 --> 00:10:27.483
And I want to tell you all this: we need to be watching.

00:10:30.899 --> 00:10:50.415
I told you all when we saw that thing happen up in Kansas—those two kids doing what they did—that was part of what I told you and tried to warn you about, about parades and big concert events.

00:10:50.415 --> 00:10:54.187
Be watchful, be prayed up, pray Psalm 91.

00:10:54.187 --> 00:11:04.320
We can draw a bloodline and take authority over the demonic agenda for mass shootings so that doesn't happen anymore.

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:09.907
It's not just about America; it's a worldwide thing.

00:11:10.049 --> 00:11:23.288
I don't know if everybody has guns everywhere, but I'm just saying to have wisdom and pray Psalm 91 for protection over where you are at all times—malls, big gatherings, whatever.

00:11:33.670 --> 00:11:38.290
I just feel to pray over this for protection because I saw a demonic agenda coming to cause havoc and confusion.

00:11:38.290 --> 00:11:41.898
We have authority over this stuff.

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:49.784
That should not have happened in Kansas.

00:11:49.784 --> 00:11:56.040
We, as the body of Christ, should start taking our dominion.

00:11:56.040 --> 00:11:59.178
We have massive warring angels.

00:11:59.178 --> 00:12:04.310
We're too devil-minded, thinking the devil has power.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:09.649
No, we have power and authority.

00:12:09.649 --> 00:12:14.381
We shouldn't be letting the devil do anything.

00:12:14.381 --> 00:12:29.013
We have power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you or your family.

00:12:29.013 --> 00:12:46.293
Every single day you wake up, pray protection around your children—pray over them going to school or a basketball game.

00:12:46.293 --> 00:12:58.942
Pray a hedge of the blood of Jesus over your children, taking communion and anointing them.

00:13:11.400 --> 00:13:11.800
I got this oil from one of the people that follow us.

00:13:23.949 --> 00:13:24.491
He has an oil company here in America, and I think that's really cool.

00:13:24.491 --> 00:13:26.724
