00:13:26.724 --> 00:13:34.774
He has all kinds of different fragrances like Rose of Sharon; I love them.

00:13:34.774 --> 00:13:37.220
But spikenard smelled really pretty.

00:13:37.220 --> 00:13:42.160
I anointed my kids with this.

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:46.060
I anoint them with oil.

00:13:46.060 --> 00:13:52.817
He says he prays over these oils, and I appreciate that.

00:14:06.858 --> 00:14:07.160
I anoint my kids and anoint them with oil; I put a bloodline over them.

00:14:10.191 --> 00:14:27.240
I just go over there and put this on my finger and say, "In the name of Jesus, I put a bloodline over you from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:31.399
No weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:43.247
" And every tongue that rises against you, we condemn it in the name of Jesus.

